## 📂 Dataset Source

The dataset is sourced from publicly available review data.  
You may find similar datasets here:
- [Skytrax Airline Reviews](https://www.airlinequality.com/)
- [Kaggle Airline Review Datasets](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets)

